text: Garde-Colombe is a commune in the Hautes-Alpes department. The municipality was created on 1 January 2016 and consists of the former communes of Eyguians (the seat), Lagrand and Saint-Genis.Arrêté préfectoral 2 October 2015 == References == Category:2016 establishments in France Category:Communes in Hautes-Alpes
title: Garde-Colombe
